    <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-brand mb-4">SEO Pricing in Swansea</h1>

    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Good news: SEO in Swansea is more affordable than most Welsh business owners expect. Monthly retainers start from £497 for small businesses and go up to £1,997 for enterprise-level campaigns. Unlike agencies in Cardiff or Bristol that pad their fees with unnecessary overheads, working with a Swansea-based team means you get strong ROI at a sensible price. Local keyword competition is lower, and because we're right here in Swansea, we can be more responsive and hands-on with the businesses we serve.</p>

    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">This page lays out exactly what you get at each price point, what one-off services cost, and how to figure out whether SEO is a worthwhile investment for your particular business. No vague quotes, no hidden fees, no nasty surprises on the invoice.</p>

    <div class="bg-rose-50 border-l-4 border-accent p-4 rounded-r-lg my-6">
      <p class="font-semibold text-text mb-1">Quick Answer</p>
      <p class="text-text/80">SEO in Swansea costs between £497 and £1,997 per month depending on how many keywords you're targeting, what content you need, and how competitive your market is. One-off audits start from £297. Every plan is rolling monthly with no lock-in. Most businesses see measurable improvements within 3-4 months.</p>
