    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Why Transparent Pricing Matters</h2>

    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Let's be honest: the SEO industry has a reputation problem. Too many agencies hide behind "bespoke quotes" and "it depends" because they want to charge whatever each client will stomach. That works for the agency, not for the business owner.</p>

    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Transparent pricing does three things. First, you can budget properly before we even have a conversation. Second, it forces us to spell out exactly what you get for your money. Third, it builds trust because there's nothing tucked away in the small print. A restaurant on <strong>Mumbles seafront</strong> and a tradesman working out of <strong>Morriston</strong> have very different budgets and very different needs. Clear tiers let each choose the right level of investment without any pressure.</p>

    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We publish our prices because we're confident in what they deliver. Every line item listed below is something we actually do each month — not padding to justify the fee. If you want to compare us with other providers, you'll find our <a href="/services/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">full service descriptions</a> just as straightforward.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Monthly SEO Plans</h2>

