    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Not sure which plan is right for you? <a href="/free-seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">Grab your free audit</a> and we'll recommend the right tier based on where you stand, who you're up against, and what you want to achieve.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">One-Off SEO Services</h2>

    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Not every business needs a monthly retainer. These standalone services give you expert insight without an ongoing commitment. Each one comes with a detailed report and prioritised actions you can implement yourself or pass to your developer.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8">
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light mb-2">SEO Audit</h3>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand">£297</span>
        </div>
