        <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">SEO in Swansea typically runs between £497 and £1,997 per month depending on scope, keyword targets, and competition. One-off audits start from £297. These prices are 20-40 percent lower than equivalent services in Cardiff or Bristol thanks to lower overheads right here in Swansea.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
