        <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Swansea has lower agency overheads and less keyword competition. Office space, salaries, and running costs are all lower, which feeds directly into lower fees without any drop in quality. Google's ranking factors are the same everywhere, so Swansea businesses get the same methodology at a better price.</p>
